Command> gh issue close

Arguments> [issue number]

TL;DR> close issue

Keywords> github
        > issue


Description>
           > $ gh issue close [issue number] [flags]
           >
           > - flags
           >    - c, comment (string)
           >    - r, reason  (string)
           >    - R, repo (HOST|OWNER|REPO)
           >
           >
           >
           >
           >


Reference> https://cli.github.com/manual/gh_issue_close
         > https://zenn.dev/gashi/articles/6a9b7bf2b9dfe79e3870
